      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOKEY CHARISMA (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (28.08) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Can bounce back. IOMMI (6) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 5 lengths (20.63). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Has ability and can atone. NITRO NED (7) was well fancied last time on the strength of a win two back but could only manage sixth (24.28) at this track. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Must be included in calculations. OUT OF TIME (2) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts ago but finished fifth last time (20.12) at Capalaba. Some good form is emerging from his last run.",
